#include<iostream>
#include<algorithm>
#include<vector>
using namespace std;

int main()
{
    long long int t;
    cin>>t;
    while(t--)
    {
        long long n;
        cin>>n;
        long long n1=n;
        long long x;
        vector<long long> v;
        while(n--)
        {
            cin>>x;
            v.push_back(x);
        }
        sort(v.begin(),v.end());
        for(long long i=0;i<n1;i++)
            cout<<v[i]<<" ";
        cout<<endl;

    }
}
